      "body" : "I would expect the one from <code>EmbeddedServletContainerCustomizer</code> to also work. But I would go what is provided instead of trying to bolt on your own. Why your solution doesn&#39;t work has to do with the default behavior programmed (accidentally?) in the <code>ServerProperties</code>, the default configured <code>contextPath</code> is <code>&quot;&quot;</code> (and it checks for <code>null</code> and not <code>&quot;&quot;</code>. The latter overrides your explicitly set <code>contextPath</code>."
