    "body" : "<p>In Spring Boot 1.5:</p>\n\n<p>Add the following property in <code>application.properties</code>:</p>\n\n<pre><code>server.context-path=/demo\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Note: <code>/demo</code> is your context path URL.</p>\n"
